      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ICE COLD SAPPORO (7) gave his opponents no chance last start when he cruised to a 13 metres victory over 2185m at this track. Tactics will be crucial from this wide draw. Meets a comparable field so he can keep the ball rolling. CURADH (11) resumes from a spell of four months after closing off last campaign in good form, the last run being a solid third over 2185m at this track. Not drawn to best so may need a 10/10 drive. Well-placed to take this out. BETTOR MOVE ALONG (8) is also high on the list of contenders despite a tough draw. Best form measures up favourably in this line-up so just needs a bit of luck to go his way. FOLLOW ROCKNROLL (1) finished sixth two runs ago then broke and finished a distant last over 2185m at this track at the latest appearance. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Won't find this any harder and he can bounce back.",
